Foreigners net buyers of Japanese stocks in week . Foreigners were net buyers of Japanese stocks on the Tokyo , Osaka and Nagoya stock exchanges in the week of June 16 to June 20 , exchange data showed . Foreigners were net buyers for the ninth consecutive week . The figures , which are rounded , are as follows : Total foreign buying 678 . 88 billion yen Total foreign selling 516 . 61 billion yen Net buying 162 . 27 billion yen Previous week net buying 244 . 11 billion yen 
